{"tid":813614,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"淡淡未日[又破頂]中國女首富5,200萬沽尚御樓王","createTime":"2018-09-10T14:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T02:02:41.000Z","uid":10101,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cc370621a1624cc2aa31862499e455eb380b8407","tid":813614,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T14:45:50.000Z","msg":"消息指，九龍塘尚御1座頂層連天台「樓王」，實用面積1,595方呎，剛以5,200萬元連車位易手，呎價32,602元，無論成交價及呎價均破盡屋苑新高。破頂賣樓的業主，正是來自湖南的「中國女首富」周群飛。<br />\n周群飛現年約48歲，在今年3月公佈的《胡潤全球白手起家女富豪榜》中，以615億元人民幣（約755億港元）身家，排名第一，財富比去年上漲45%。土地註冊處資料顯示，周於2010年向長實（1113）買入該尚御物業，當時成交價已高達4,781萬元，呎價近3萬元已是當年樓盤的頂峰價。是次沽出單位，8年賬面賺約419萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180910/58666876\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180910%2F58666876&d=ZjsqiCRAtuumaJOgmOTu9%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=2ee5eb54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180910%2F58666876&h=5e780207\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180910/58666876</a>"},{"pid":"277b9d266363b26f3eb9feebf9adfee93de7c5db","tid":813614,"uid":18955,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:24:18.000Z","msg":"8年先賺一成<br />\n對佢黎講可能蝕讓<br />\n<br />\n不過錢存係香港點都安全啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f66214d15d2487f801bc0704e2cee7a4ba01eb07","tid":813614,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T16:30:11.000Z","msg":"其實算好平<br />\n個天台同車位都值1000萬"},{"pid":"fdff69d672c4424d21fdc660692631d095941a75","tid":813614,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T16:47:48.000Z","msg":"一年升1％ 業主又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a656df61c2afa1089ba687eb485daeef9a0b56c8","tid":813614,"uid":154415,"like":0,